These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, black, chestnut, white
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
3. the person who likes blood-red is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
5. the person who likes blood-red is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Color   | chestnut | white      | blood-red | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, emerald, turquise, coral
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the person who likes emerald is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | coral | turquise | emerald   | white |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
4 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, chinchilla, pony
1. the person eating corn is the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Pet   | horse  | pony   | chinchilla | lizard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, folk, hip-hop
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of reggae##2
4. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
5. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | folk     | reggae    | salsa       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, may, june, december
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Birthday   | may  | december | january | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
House: colonial, tower, palace, gothic-revival
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
3. the gothic-revival house is between the police-officer and the palace house##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| House   | palace        | gothic-revival     | colonial       | tower   |

