.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, domino, bridge
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the person playing billiard and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
5. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
6. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Game   | billiard | canasta  | domino  | bridge   |
| Pet           | turtle  | goldfish | snake | hamster |

