.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Pet    | mouse | frog  | horse | goldfish |

