2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Pet       | mouse       | hamster   | rabbit | turtle |

