.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, go, billiard
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
5. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| Game      | domino  | billiard | mah-jongg | go |

