.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, freelancer, electrician, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the electrician##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the musician is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the electrician is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | firefighter | freelancer   | electrician | musician     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

