.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
City: edinburgh, new-york, london, hamburg
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the person traveling to london##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| City         | london  | hamburg | edinburgh | new-york |

