.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, woodworking, writing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, trike, ship
1. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
3. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing | dancing | camping |
| Transport   | boat     | ship  | subway  | trike    |

