.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, thriller, western
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, board-games, baking, writing
1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | disaster | documentary | thriller |
| Hobby   | baking | reading | board-games   | writing  |

