.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, july, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, manager, mechanic
1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in september##2
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Birthday   | march | july  | october      | september |
| Job     | manager    | mechanic | entrepreneur | analyst   |

