.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, sprite, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: american, nigerian, polish, mexican
1. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the mexican##1
4. the american is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
6. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking cola and the nigerian##2
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite  | fanta      | tea       |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | nigerian | american |

