.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
4 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, domino, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, tram
1. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person playing domino is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Game   | billiard     | scrabble | bridge | domino |
| Transport     | helicopter | bike    | taxi    | tram |

