.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, mah-jongg, go
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person playing bridge is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person playing snooker##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
3. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game         | mah-jongg   | go   | bridge       | snooker   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | helicopter | snowmobile |

