.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indonesian, pakistani, polish
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the polish##1
3. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| Nationality   | pakistani | polish | indonesian      | french        |

 